OL,4,CUnions criticise 'miserly' 50p rise in
OL,5,Cstatutory sick pay
OL,6, Unions have criticised a 50p-per-week
OL,7, increase in statutory sick pay (SSP) as
OL,8, "miserly".
OL,10,FSSP increases from #95.85 to #96.35 on
OL,11,FTuesday, but unions including the
OL,12,FTrades Union Congress (TUC) and Unite
OL,13,Fsay it is too little to live on.
OL,15,FTUC general secretary Frances O'Grady
OL,16,Fsaid: "No one should be plunged into
OL,17,Fhardship if they need to self-isolate."
OL,19,FA government spokesman said there was a
OL,20,F"comprehensive package" in place to
OL,21,Fsupport those who need to self-isolate.
